From b874374f0a29e7bd5313d343c402fe0d4ced5616 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Wed, 4 Feb 2026 18:47:31 +1100
Subject: [PATCH 032/118] arm64: dts: cix: Set O6N DP PHY to pure DisplayPort
 mode

Set usbc_phy3 default_conf to UDPHY_MODE_DP (0x02) on Orion O6N.
This port is a dedicated DP output, not USB-C combo, so the PHY
should not wait for USB role negotiation.

Fixes DP output not working on O6N. Same pattern as usbc_phy1 on O6
which drives the HDMI bridge.

Reported-by: community testing

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts
index d03c98da843ca..443c29753432b 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/cix/sky1-orion-o6n.dts
@@ -1638,6 +1638,7 @@ &usbss_2 {
 
 &usbc_phy3 {
 	status = "okay";
+	default_conf = /bits/ 8 <0x02>;  /* UDPHY_MODE_DP - pure DP output */
 };
 
 &usb3_phy3 {
-- 
